{"id": "software-development--custom-public-key-searcher", "title": "Custom public key searcher", "forum": "software-development", "messages": [{"id": "1403813033481863168", "author": "Random Citizen", "author_handle": "caelkash_10391", "user_id": "1166695934684569612", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1166695934684569612/267979e9f55553218d72fe739dfcb326.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 2:51 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 2:51 p.m.", "text": "I needed something to create a custom pubkey for my repeater (and my companion to look \"cool\") so I cooked up this. Sharing for anyone who prefers a little customization over security. https://github.com/liquidraver/MCKeySearcher", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I needed something to create a custom pubkey for my repeater (and my companion to look &quot;cool&quot;) so I cooked up this. Sharing for anyone who prefers a little customization over security.\n\n<a href=\"https://github.com/liquidraver/MCKeySearcher\">https://github.com/liquidraver/MCKeySearcher</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=metal><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=🤘 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f918.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1403814832100348056", "author": "Uncle Lit", "author_handle": "unclelit", "user_id": "84097297872322560", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 2:58 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 2:58 p.m.", "text": "Thanks for sharing this!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Thanks for sharing this!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1403818982762479708", "author": "Random Citizen", "author_handle": "caelkash_10391", "user_id": "1166695934684569612", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1166695934684569612/267979e9f55553218d72fe739dfcb326.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 3:15 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 3:15 p.m.", "text": "just a heads up, if you search for two characters for prefix and only need one key, you'll likely get at least 6. or if your CPU is fast, you can get 768", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>just a heads up, if you search for two characters for prefix and only need one key, you&#39;ll likely get at least 6. or if your CPU is fast, you can get 768 <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😄\"\n    title=\"smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f604.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1403822628514566225", "author": "Uncle Lit", "author_handle": "unclelit", "user_id": "84097297872322560", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 3:29 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 3:29 p.m.", "text": "i am going to run this on WSL on my 5950X", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>i am going to run this on WSL on my 5950X</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1403823304745422979", "author": "Random Citizen", "author_handle": "caelkash_10391", "user_id": "1166695934684569612", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1166695934684569612/267979e9f55553218d72fe739dfcb326.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 3:32 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 3:32 p.m.", "text": "the program will give you an estimate how many seconds/days/years your search will take", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>the program will give you an estimate how many seconds/days/years your search will take <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"🙂\"\n    title=\"slight_smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f642.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1403832451591311360", "author": "Uncle Lit", "author_handle": "unclelit", "user_id": "84097297872322560", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 4:08 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 4:08 p.m.", "text": "I had to change the makefile -I$(ED25519_DIR) to -I$(ED25519_DIR)/src' for make pgo-generate` to run without error. the ed25519.h file was not found (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I had to change the makefile\n\n<code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">-I$(ED25519_DIR)</code> \n\nto \n\n<code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">-I$(ED25519_DIR)/src&#39;\n\nfor </code>make pgo-generate` to run without error.  the ed25519.h file was not found</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, August 9, 2025 4:13 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1403834360909533277", "author": "Random Citizen", "author_handle": "caelkash_10391", "user_id": "1166695934684569612", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1166695934684569612/267979e9f55553218d72fe739dfcb326.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, August 9, 2025 4:16 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-08-09 4:16 p.m.", "text": "odd, I was testing it with WSLUbuntu and it was working. anyway, WSL takes away a lot of power from the CPU, so if you are searching for more sophistocated keys, that's something to consider that pgo-generate was never truly tested, it doesn't added noticeable keys/sec for me on WSL and did not have the time yet to test it on native linux", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>odd, I was testing it with WSLUbuntu and it was working.\n\nanyway, WSL takes away a lot of power from the CPU, so if you are searching for more sophistocated keys, that&#39;s something to consider\n\nthat pgo-generate was never truly tested, it doesn&#39;t added noticeable keys/sec for me on WSL and did not have the time yet to test it on native linux</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/84097297872322560/6096864cb914ce2cbf40ded0a3f9c081.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=unclelit>Uncle Lit</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1403832451591311360')\"> I had to change the makefile\n\n<code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">-I$(ED25519_DIR)</code> \n\nto \n\n<code class=\"chatlog__markdown-pre chatlog__markdown-pre--inline\">-I$(ED25519_DIR)/src&#39;\n\nfor </code>make pgo-generate` to run without error.  the ed25519.h file was not found </span> <span class=chatlog__reply-edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, August 9, 2025 4:13 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, 